1
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:20,560
Hey,

2
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,280
did you hear?

3
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:21,960
What happened?

4
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,840
I heard the paper bride killed someone again.

5
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,360
Ah.

6
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:26,600
The inpatient department brought in a vegetative patient this morning.

7
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,960
Can the paper bride really kill?

8
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,720
You go to the inpatient department.

9
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:30,380
I'll check the surveillance.

10
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,479
Play that part again.

11
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:45,440
Master.

12
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,360
I'm at the hospital right now.

13
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:47,720
Ah.

14
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:50,039
Another paper bride appeared here.

15
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:50,810
Another one.

16
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,160
It's never-ending.

17
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:55,640
We haven't even finished the first two cases.

18
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,320
What's the situation this time?

19
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,440
They said they lost a

20
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,900
male vegetative patient.

21
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,240
I'm checking the surveillance.

22
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,500
A vegetative patient?

23
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,160
Can he still be saved?

24
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,640
Let's not worry about that now.

25
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,480
The doctor said

26
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,800
if we find him within half an hour,

27
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,759
he can still be saved.

28
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,560
He is still breathing on his own.

29
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:16,720
Stop.

30
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:17,960
Zoom in.

31
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,640
Xiao Zhai.

32
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,160
I'll send you a photo now.

33
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,760
Immediately pull up the surveillance

34
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,320
of all the streets around the hospital.

35
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,280
We must find this person.

36
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:28,680
Got it?

37
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,850
Zoom in, zoom in.

38
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,880
Officer.

39
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,360
Ever since he married that shameless Qi Xiaoling,

40
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,240
my son

41
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,960
has attempted suicide no less than five times.

42
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,160
But only this time

43
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,160
did he end up in the hospital.

44
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:48,880
Who knows

45
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,160
if she did it.

46
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:51,920
Or maybe

47
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,700
it was done by some man she hooked up with.

48
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,360
Officer.

49
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:59,280
I also thought it was fishy at first.

50
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,400
I originally

51
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,360
wanted to call the police.

52
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,160
But

53
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,080
my wife felt embarrassed,

54
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,440
so she stopped me.

55
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:06,960
Sigh.

56
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,420
What's fishy about it?

57
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,970
When we went there this morning...

58
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,440
Help!

59
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,480
Help!

60
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,560
I was just busy saving someone.

61
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,320
Later, when I opened the package,

62
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,320
there was a paper bride inside, too.

63
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,360
Hey.

64
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,800
That paper bride,

65
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,960
do you still have it?

66
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,360
Ah, yes, it's still here.

67
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,560
Give me your detailed home address.

68
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,360
We will go over to collect evidence later.

69
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,520
Ah, okay, okay.

70
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,820
Hello, Master.

71
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,090
Surveillance shows

72
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:56,010
that the cleaner finally disappeared in Yangguang Neighborhood.

73
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,960
Zhou Zheng and Qi Xiaoling live in this neighborhood.

74
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,660
Take a look at this.

75
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,260
This is the surveillance footage

76
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,600
from my hospital.

77
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:19,399
People who engage in specific physical labor for a long time

78
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,200
will have marks on their bodies.

79
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,320
Look.

80
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:26,880
Judging from the curvature of her spine and her special gait,

81
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:30,040
this person should be a real cleaner.

82
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,850
And this person,

83
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,200
we all know.

84
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,520
It's Zhao Wen.

85
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,320
Jiang A 5C896.

86
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:42,720
Jiang A 5C896.

87
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,960
Hey, what are you doing?

88
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,640
Police.

89
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,159
Oh.

90
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,159
Sir,

91
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:49,560
is there a cleaner in your neighborhood named Zhao Wen?

92
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:49,960
Zhao Wen?

93
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,360
Oh,

94
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,220
I know Zhao Wen.

95
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,080
She's been cleaning here for a while.

96
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:55,800
Buildings 5 and 6 are for both commercial and residential use.

97
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,800
There are many small companies and shops inside.

98
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,159
Zhao Wen cleans

99
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,160
for more than a dozen of them.

100
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,160
More than a dozen?

101
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,810
Hello, Zhai.

102
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,520
Contact Zhao Wen's cleaning company immediately.

103
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,760
Get all the addresses where she provides cleaning services,

104
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,360
and send them to me right away.

105
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,090
Understood?

106
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,410
Okay, do it fast.

107
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,480
Hi.

108
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,400
Police.

109
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,140
Have you seen this person?

110
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,360
She's a cleaner in your neighborhood.

111
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,220
Never seen her.

112
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,340
Okay, sorry to bother you.

113
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:48,760
Hello.

114
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,600
I'm from the Public Security Bureau.

115
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,680
Is there someone named Zhao Wen

116
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,240
who cleans your place?

117
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,360
No.

118
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,210
Then please take a look.

119
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,720
Have you seen this person?

120
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:03,840
No.

121
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,050
Are you sure?

122
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,020
Never seen her.

123
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,920
Alright, sorry to bother you.

124
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,600
It's fine.

125
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,400
Hello.

126
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:36,600
What's the matter?

127
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,060
Have you seen this person?

128
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,120
A cleaner.

129
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,000
No.

130
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
It's too dark to see clearly.

131
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,400
Hey, Captain Gu.

132
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,480
I've checked the eight households here.

133
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,010
Nothing.

134
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,980
This is the last one for me too.

135
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:09,770
Nothing either.

136
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:10,800
Yeah.

137
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:12,960
Hurry up.

138
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,040
We must find Zhou Zheng quickly.

139
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,440
These two parallel wheel tracks

140
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,640
should be left by a large sanitation trash can.

141
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,400
The footprints next to it vary in depth,

142
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,810
and the stride is messy.

143
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,080
It shows this person was dragging a heavy object,

144
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,409
physically exhausted,

145
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:37,380
and constantly adjusting their direction and center of gravity.

146
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,720
Can't open it.

147
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,600
Hold this.

148
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,360
At critical moments,

149
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,880
we have to rely on this.

150
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,680
Hurry up.

151
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,600
Zhao Wen.

152
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,330
Don't come over.

153
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:06,120
Put the knife down.

154
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,180
Put down the knife.

155
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,770
Don't come over.

156
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,050
Think about your daughter.

157
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,120
I did this for my daughter.

158
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,920
That beast said

159
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:22,120
he would take our whole family to die with him sooner or later.

160
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,360
Why?

161
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,640
What did I do wrong?

162
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:29,040
And what did my daughter do wrong?

163
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,760
He's the one who sinned.

164
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,650
If anyone is going to die, it should be him.

165
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,440
Zhang Song is already dead.

166
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,500
He won't hurt your daughter anymore.

167
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,360
But what you're doing now

168
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,540
is likely to bring her a lifetime of pain.

169
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,220
Zhao Wen, listen to me.

170
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,800
If you stab him,

171
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,290
that's intentional homicide.

172
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,770
It's the death penalty.

173
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,490
If you give me the knife,

174
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,090
it's attempted murder,

175
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:03,690
and your sentence can be reduced appropriately.

176
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,820
Zhang Song is dead.

177
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,680
If something happens to you,

178
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,740
your daughter will become an orphan.

179
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,440
Zhao Wen.

180
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,520
My mother

181
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,080
passed away when I was seven.

182
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,560
Every year since then on my birthday,

183
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,680
I think of her.

184
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,860
The other day in the counseling room,

185
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,810
when your daughter was filling out the form, I saw

186
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:38,330
that her birthday is in three days.

187
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,540
Don't you want to continue watching her grow up?

188
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,480
Hello, Mrs. Rong.

189
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,540
Is Qingqing there?

190
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,700
Her mother is looking for her.

191
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,760
Mom.

192
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,600
I'm still here at Ms. An's.

193
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:11,360
She just asked me what my dream is.

194
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,620
I thought about it.

195
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,800
I don't really want anything.

196
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:17,240
I just want to live an ordinary life with you,

197
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,480
just the two of us.

198
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:47,800
Master.

199
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:50,720
We just searched Zhou Zheng's house

200
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:53,320
and found some ropes and a dozen suicide notes.

201
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,320
It seems he often attempts suicide.

202
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,000
Otherwise,

203
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,330
he wouldn't keep these things around.

204
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,960
The ligature mark on Zhou Zheng's neck is horseshoe-shaped.

205
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,400
It's deeper at the bottom

206
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,800
and fades towards the top.

207
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:08,840
It does look like suicide.

208
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,210
The problem lies with the rope.

209
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:15,090
I checked Zhou Zheng's purchase history.

210
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:18,160
He frequently bought this type of rope online.

211
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:24,440
Here,

212
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,560
come.

213
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,400
Hey.

214
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,600
Hey.

215
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,180
Hold tight.

216
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,160
What are you doing?

217
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,560
Hold it.

218
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:55,120
Hey.

219
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,920
Zhai.

220
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:56,400
Zhai.

221
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,730
He wasn't really trying to die,

222
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,280
but kidnapping.

223
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,010
Kidnapping?

224
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,530
Who's kidnapping whom?

225
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,960
Qi Xiaoling.

226
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,000
It's a kind of moral kidnapping,

227
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,650
or you could call it emotional blackmail.

228
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:22,120
Zhou Zheng wanted to use fake suicide

229
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,250
to keep Qi Xiaoling by his side.

230
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,880
This special rope

231
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,200
breaks when it reaches a certain tension.

232
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,400
It can't kill anyone.

233
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:32,760
But that

234
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,760
normal rope

235
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,620
is what almost got Zhou Zheng killed.

236
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:40,650
This was obviously swapped out secretly.

237
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,740
It was Zhao Wen.

238
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,440
On the rope Zhou Zheng used to commit suicide,

239
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,170
did you find her fingerprints?

240
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,880
There were no fingerprints.

241
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:51,450
But I detected dimethyl siloxane.

242
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,140
It's a component of floor wax.

243
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:04,120
It seems Zhao Wen did touch this rope.

244
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,000
Wait.

245
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,920
But why would she do this?

246
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,490
Definitely not out of boredom.

247
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,050
Let's interrogate her.

248
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:26,960
Zhao Wen.

249
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,290
Why did you kill Zhou Zheng?

250
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,490
Because he deserved to die.

251
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,160
How did you meet Zhou Zheng?

252
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,480
I met him when I was working as a cleaner.

253
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,440
You are lying.

254
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:42,560
The cleaning company confirmed

255
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:45,080
that Zhou Zheng's family never hired a cleaner.

256
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,410
All the housework was done by Qi Xiaoling.

257
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,290
Do you know Qi Xiaoling?

258
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:51,840
No.

259
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,680
Raise your head.

260
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,440
Look at me.

261
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,850
Think about your daughter.

262
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,080
She is only seven.

263
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:06,600
If someone instructed you to do this,

264
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,360
I hope you can confess to us

265
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:10,660
and try to get a lighter sentence.

266
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,120
No.

267
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,600
No one ordered me to do it.

268
00:14:19,880 --> 00:14:21,000
I'm sorry, Qi Xiaoling.

269
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,200
Sorry for taking up your time.

270
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,120
We have a situation.

271
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,520
We need to ask you some questions.

272
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:25,000
Okay.

273
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,360
Qi Xiaoling.

274
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,640
The night Zhou Zheng committed suicide,

275
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:37,500
where were you?

276
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:40,060
We had a fight that day.

277
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,600
A pretty bad one.

278
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,730
Then I went to stay at a hotel by myself.

279
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,930
You can check the hotel's surveillance footage.

280
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:49,000
There's someone named Zhao Wen.

281
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,860
Do you know her?

282
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:52,960
No, I don't.

283
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,960
I heard

284
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:58,800
she's been working as a cleaner in your neighborhood.

285
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,660
Think about it. Have you seen her?

286
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,200
I still don't know her, Officer.

287
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,760
I'm not the neighborhood security guard.

288
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,560
Am I supposed to know everyone

289
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:11,420
who frequents our neighborhood?

290
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,040
Mm.

291
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:14,760
Your husband often threatened to commit suicide.

292
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:15,960
You know that, right?

293
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,040
Yes.

294
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,040
He was just playing around.

295
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:22,080
But someone switched the rope he used to kill himself.

296
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:26,040
Did you know that?

297
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:29,480
I didn't know.

298
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:31,880
Officer,

299
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,820
are you suspecting me?

300
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:38,240
How is it?

301
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,130
Did she confess?

302
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:40,960
No.

303
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:43,370
She refused to admit it.

304
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,800
But I still feel

305
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:47,020
that they know each other.

306
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:48,920
I have an idea.

307
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:03,560
You have to force me, right?

308
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,560
Then let's try it.

309
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:05,080
Stop it.

310
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:05,810
Give it to me.

311
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,320
Give it to me.
